<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tenant Estoppel Certificate Request - {{deal.name}}</title>
</head>
<body>
  {{> header documentTitle="Estoppel Certificate Request" documentStatus=version.status documentVersion=version.version}}

  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-info">
      <strong>{{deal.buyerName}}</strong><br>
      {{deal.buyerAddress}}<br>
      {{deal.buyerCity}}, {{deal.buyerState}} {{deal.buyerZip}}
    </div>
    <div class="date">{{date generatedAt 'long'}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="document-title">
    <h1>TENANT ESTOPPEL CERTIFICATE REQUEST</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="property-info">
    <strong>RE: {{deal.name}}</strong><br>
    {{deal.propertyAddress}}, {{deal.city}}, {{deal.state}} {{deal.zipCode}}
  </div>

  <div class="letter-body">
    <p>Dear Property Management / Landlord:</p>

    <p>
      In connection with the pending sale of the above-referenced property, we respectfully
      request that you obtain and deliver executed Tenant Estoppel Certificates from
      {{#if estoppel.specificTenants}}the tenants listed below{{else}}all tenants{{/if}}
      at the Property.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please use the attached form of Estoppel Certificate. The completed certificates should
      be returned no later than <strong>{{date estoppel.dueDate 'long'}}</strong>.
    </p>

    <h3>REQUIRED ESTOPPELS</h3>

    {{#if estoppel.specificTenants}}
    <table class="tenant-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Unit</th>
          <th>Tenant Name</th>
          <th>Lease Expiration</th>
          <th>Monthly Rent</th>
          <th>Status</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each tenants}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{this.unitNumber}}</td>
          <td>{{this.tenantName}}</td>
          <td>{{date this.leaseEnd 'short'}}</td>
          <td>{{currency this.currentRent}}</td>
          <td class="status-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {{else}}
    <p>
      Estoppel Certificates are required from <strong>all tenants</strong> currently
      occupying the Property. Per the rent roll dated {{date rentRoll.asOfDate 'short'}},
      this includes <strong>{{rentRoll.occupiedUnits}} units</strong>.
    </p>
    {{/if}}

    <h3>DELIVERY INSTRUCTIONS</h3>
    <p>Please return all executed Estoppel Certificates to:</p>
    <div class="delivery-info">
      <strong>{{deal.buyerContact}}</strong><br>
      {{deal.buyerName}}<br>
      Email: {{deal.buyerEmail}}<br>
      {{#if deal.buyerFax}}Fax: {{deal.buyerFax}}{{/if}}
    </div>

    <p>
      If you have any questions regarding the Estoppel Certificates or require additional
      copies of the attached form, please contact the undersigned.
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>

    <p class="closing">
      Sincerely,<br><br><br>
      _______________________________<br>
      {{deal.buyerContact}}<br>
      {{deal.buyerName}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-break"></div>

  {{!-- ESTOPPEL CERTIFICATE FORM --}}
  <div class="estoppel-form">
    <h1>TENANT ESTOPPEL CERTIFICATE</h1>

    <div class="form-intro">
      <p>
        The undersigned tenant ("Tenant") hereby certifies to <strong>{{deal.buyerName}}</strong>
        ("Buyer"), and its lenders, successors, and assigns, as follows in connection with the
        pending acquisition of the property located at:
      </p>
      <div class="property-reference">
        {{deal.propertyAddress}}, {{deal.city}}, {{deal.state}} {{deal.zipCode}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-section">
      <h3>1. LEASE INFORMATION</h3>
      <table class="form-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Tenant Name:</td>
          <td class="input-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Unit/Suite Number:</td>
          <td class="input-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Premises Square Footage:</td>
          <td class="input-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Lease Commencement Date:</td>
          <td class="input-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Lease Expiration Date:</td>
          <td class="input-cell"></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Current Monthly Base Rent:</td>
          <td class="input-cell">$</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Additional Rent/CAM (Monthly):</td>
          <td class="input-cell">$</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Security Deposit Held:</td>
          <td class="input-cell">$</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="form-section">
      <h3>2. LEASE STATUS CERTIFICATIONS</h3>
      <p>Tenant certifies that:</p>
      <ol class="cert-list">
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            The Lease is in full force and effect and has not been modified, amended, or
            supplemented, except as follows (if none, write "None"):
            <div class="input-line"></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Tenant is in possession of the Premises and is open for business.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Rent has been paid through: _______________ and no rent has been paid more than
            one month in advance.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            To Tenant's knowledge, neither Landlord nor Tenant is in default under the Lease,
            and no event has occurred which, with the passage of time or giving of notice,
            would constitute a default.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Tenant has no claims, defenses, or offsets against rent or other charges due
            under the Lease.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Tenant has no options to purchase the Premises or any right of first refusal
            regarding the sale of the Property, except as follows (if none, write "None"):
            <div class="input-line"></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Tenant has no renewal or extension options except as follows (if none, write "None"):
            <div class="input-line"></div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Landlord has completed all tenant improvement work required under the Lease.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            Tenant has not assigned the Lease or sublet any portion of the Premises.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="checkbox">&#9744;</span>
            No bankruptcy, insolvency, reorganization, or similar proceedings are pending
            or threatened against Tenant.
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="form-section">
      <h3>3. ADDITIONAL INFORMATION</h3>
      <p>Please provide any additional comments or clarifications:</p>
      <div class="comments-box"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-section">
      <h3>4. CERTIFICATION</h3>
      <p>
        The undersigned certifies that the information provided herein is true, complete,
        and accurate as of the date set forth below. This Certificate may be relied upon
        by Buyer and its lenders in connection with the acquisition and financing of the Property.
      </p>

      <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-header">TENANT:</div>
          <div class="input-line wide"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Print Name of Tenant/Entity</div>

          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Authorized Signature</div>

          <div class="input-line"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Print Name and Title</div>

          <div class="input-line"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Date</div>

          <div class="input-line"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Phone Number</div>

          <div class="input-line"></div>
          <div class="signature-label">Email Address</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-footer">
      <p class="disclaimer">
        <strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> This Estoppel Certificate is being provided in connection
        with the sale of the Property. Any misrepresentation may result in liability to the
        Buyer and its lenders.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{> footer documentTitle="Estoppel Certificate Request" documentVersion=version.version}}
</body>
</html>

<style>
